Spasstik's metalic paws continued to beat against the African soil as he
moved further and further away from the battle scene, with the valuable
welker rifle in his maw. Rasor sharp claws propelled him forward,
tearing up the earth, as herds of animals scattered to make room for the
larger than normal wolf. He was almost at the edge of the continent,
where he was to rendezvous with Astrotain, and hopefully he would show
up, for lack of flight could keep him grounded on this rock.
